name: Patricia Horoho
description: Looking for someone to share this next phase of my life, I think of myself as warm, friendly, relaxed and easy going, I would like to find someone who I can be very comfortable with I have been alone for a long time, so far I have not found anything good about being alone, I am trustworthy, caring, sincere, honest, loyal, romantic a good attitude with a good sense of humor and guess what I have a wonderful personality I am easy going, I am in good shape and good health.
